    {
      "chinese": "「女人當家；男人守衛部落」是早期卑南族男女在社會地位上存在的普遍現象。當時的女性是以農耕、飼養為主要職務，平時還要做烹調、搗米及育兒的工作，可以說所有的家務事都由女性來操守。",
      "ab": "“na vavayan mu, maw na kazu i ruma’ zi, na ma’inayan mu, maw na ma’iyar kana zekalr” aziyu ziya na vavayan mu, muwa’uma zi venavaaw kana vinavaaw, demaderu zi temusaasiyaw, panaanadam kana tu lralrak zi remarames, inia mu, nintaw kiyakarunan. numan mu, matrinanapan. aruwa ta kemani marengay. na kiyakarunan ziya i savak mu, maw na vavayan na kiyakarun.",
